title: 2013 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 50)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2013 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

We have now shared 1,455 releases amongst ourselves this year.  That finally tops my 2012 total of 1,436 releases.  In doing so, it meets the personal goal I set for myself when starting to torrent these Christian Music bundles last January.  That said, a special note of thanks to everyone who sticks around and continues to share/seed long after their download is complete.  We all play a small part in spreading His word through this medium.  And I'd like to sincerely thank you for playing your part.

The genre breakdown for today's 50th bundle might look something like this...

POP: Anthem Lights.  HIP-HOP/RAP: Beautiful Eulogy, JayKidd, Jonathan Baker, Kadence, KhingKloud, Living For God, Nine Up, Radio Roman.  CHRISTMAS: Christafari, Dave Barnes, Susan Boyle.  PRAISE & WORSHIP: Hillsong United, Jon Thurlow, Papyrus.  HARDCORE/METAL: Meadows, This Divided World, Witness.  ALTENATIVE: October Glory, Scott Stapp.  ROCK: P.O.D, Stryper, Travis Schooler.  JAZZ: Thomas Kennerk.
